rks [ revised &amp; updated ]<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The updated scope-of=
-works attached has been created as a proposed inclusive response to the fin=
dings of all the documents attached.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">While you are review=
ing the attachments, I would like to propose that I begin the process of obt=
aining repair proposals from Tower approved builders to progress the claim a=
s quickly as possible.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">If I send out the sc=
ope of works now and offer to meet with the tender respondents onsite, we ma=
y well have some preliminary costings to hand prior to the end of the busine=
ss year.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please confirm your a=
pproval for me to begin the process of preliminary pricing now.<o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Best Regards,<o:p></=
