<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hi Stephen,<o:p></o:=
p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Below is a copy of a=
n email which I sent to all parties this afternoon outlaying the expected ti=
me frames of the results which will be available to be shared with all regar=
ding test results from 23 Mays Street,
 Devonport.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Prior to receiving t=
he report from the forensic testing =E2=80=93 I am keen to take whatever ste=
ps I can to progress the claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Preliminary results a=
nd findings suggest that we may have a relatively complete understanding of w=
hat the final scope of works will be to fully remediate the property under t=
he claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">If we accept on a pr=
eliminary basis that the scope of works required to remediate the property i=
s
<b><u>generally defined</u></b> as follows:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Basement Level</s=
pan></u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4"><span style=
=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and decontaminate all exposed internal brick sur=
faces to ground level of dwelling<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoList=
Paragraph" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt=
">Replace charred timber framework to midfloor structure and ground floor wa=
lls as required<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D=
"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Rebuild rear deck=
 and steps to match existing
