evel1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Replace all hardwood decking bo=
ards to internal balcony
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l1 l=
evel1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and encapsulate all timbe=
r structural components to ground-floor walls and midfloor structure as requ=
ired<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:=
