<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l1 l=
evel1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Replace ceiling linings to grou=
nd floor as required<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" st=
yle=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Supply and i=
nstall rear pedestrian door to rear of ground floor<o:p></o:p></span></li><l=
