</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello Raffaella,</sp=
an><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you for the em=
ail below.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We can confirm that t=
esting can commence at 2pm on Friday October 17.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We will test from sa=
mple sites as required to complete a full and thorough determination of any p=
otential contamination, inclusive of all the areas which you have referred t=
o below.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You may undertake yo=
ur own independent testing at any stage; however, Tower would only consider r=
eimbursement for testing which is - a) claim related &amp; b) testing which i=
s outside of that which Tower will
 complete.<span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><o:p></o=
:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am confident that t=
he Tower Insurance testing will be transparent, quantified by lab results, a=
nd adequate to provide comfort for all parties.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clarified scope o=
f testing as follows:</span></u><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0in" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso=
-list:l10 level1 lfo11">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">150mm diameter inspection portals cut in wa=
ll cavities of every room on the first floor at a height of 300 mm of floor l=
evel and directly underneath the top plate.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D=
"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l10 le=
vel1 lfo11">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Testing of the roof cavity at the soffit ju=
nction where potential contaminants may have risen through the wall cavity. T=
esting of the roof cavity at the apex where smoke may have accumulated.</spa=
n><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;mar=
gin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l10 level1 lfo11">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Testing of the underside of the rear large u=
pper deck.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mar=
gin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l10 level1 lfo11">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Testing of the basement utilizing all expos=
ed framing cavities and 150mm testing portals cut into any remining ceiling l=
inings in the basemen area.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagr=
aph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l10 level1 lfo11">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Any additional sample sites that we feel ar=
e required during testing. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></li></ol>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">To ensure effectu=
al testing it would be beneficial if you could confirm the following:</span>=
</u><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0in" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso=
-list:l3 level1 lfo12">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">That the chlorine was located in the laundr=
y room downstairs at the time of the fire.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D=
"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l3 lev=
el1 lfo12">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The quantity of the chlorine that was in th=
at room at the time of the fire.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListP=
aragraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo12=
">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Where there any<span class=3D"apple-convert=
ed-space">&nbsp;</span><u>other chemicals</u><span class=3D"apple-converted-=
space">&nbsp;</span>that were located in that same room, or anywhere else do=
wnstairs. &nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></li></ol>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Beyond completing te=
sting and providing laboratory results as described above, I am certain the m=
ost productive action we can make towards progressing the claim is to have a=
 meeting where we can discuss the
 overall claim response process, providing a forum for you to table any ques=
tions, or concerns that you may hold. Those concerns can be responded to, an=
d the responses can be documented via minutes with actions and agreements de=
tailed in the minutes providing
 a framework for moving forward with a pre-agreed and productive pathway. I b=
elieve this would be very worthwhile and will provide us all with detail, cl=
arity, and documentation that we can all use to our benefit.</span><o:p></o:=
p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Your lawyers and adv=
isors would of course be welcome to attend this meeting.</span><o:p></o:p></=
p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I look forward to se=
eing you again on Friday.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Kind Regards,</span>=
<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant. &nbsp;&nbsp;&=
nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>
