<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;=
Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">From:</span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-spa=
ce"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-ser=
if">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ca=
libri&quot;,sans-serif">Raffaella
 del Prete &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:raffaellanz@icloud.com">raffaellanz@icloud.=
com</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Sent:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Friday, Octob=
er 10, 2025 4:53 PM<br>
<b>To:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Grant Metson &l=
t;<a href=3D"mailto:Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz">Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz</a>&g=
t;<br>
<b>Cc:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Abigail Collin &=
lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Abigail.Collin@wynnwilliams.co.nz">Abigail.Collin@wynnw=
illiams.co.nz</a>&gt;; Richard Hargreaves &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Richard.Harg=
reaves@wynnwilliams.co.nz">Richard.Hargreaves@wynnwilliams.co.nz</a>&gt;;
 Bryan Strong &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Bryan.Strong@tower.co.nz">Bryan.Strong@t=
ower.co.nz</a>&gt;; Kelly Mason &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Kelly.Mason@tower.co.n=
z">Kelly.Mason@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;; Chris Cornwall &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Chr=
is.Cornwall@tower.co.nz">Chris.Cornwall@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;;
 Megan Jensen &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Megan.Jensen@tower.co.nz">Megan.Jensen@t=
ower.co.nz</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Subject:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Re: C90306=
048 - Fire at 23 Mays Street, Devonport [WW-ACTIVE.FID3167762]</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:white">Kia ora G=
rant, Thank you for your email and for confirming receipt of our letter. Fri=
day, 17 October after 2:</span><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;font-family:&q=
uot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:white">=E2=80=8A</span><span style=3D"font-=
size:1.0pt;color:white">00
 pm works for me, and I=E2=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment co=
uld be scheduled accordingly. I also reserve my right to undertake</span><o:=
p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:white">&nbsp;</s=
pan><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Kia ora Grant,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Thank you for your email and for confirming receipt o=
f our letter.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Friday, 17 October after 2:00 pm works for me, and I=E2=
=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment could be scheduled according=
ly.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I also reserve my right to undertake independent test=
ing and assessment of the property to ensure a full and impartial evaluation=
.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Having reviewed the proposed plan, I=E2=80=99m concer=
ned the current testing schedule appears incomplete. It does not include the=
 first floor, roof cavity, or the large upper deck, and the basement coverag=
e seems partial, given the known extent
 of smoke, water, and chemical contamination.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I therefore request confirmation that the planned ins=
pection and sampling will be expanded to include all levels and relevant str=
uctural areas. Alternatively, please confirm that Tower will meet my reasona=
ble costs should I need to arrange
 independent specialists to carry out supplementary testing (including labor=
atory analysis).<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Please confirm the final timing for the 17th and the r=
evised scope of testing once available.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Ng=C4=81 mihi,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Raffaella<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<blockquote style=3D"margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt">
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">On 8 Oct 2025, at 5:26<span style=3D"font-family:&quo=
t;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">=E2=80=AF</span>PM, Grant Metson &lt;<a href=3D"ma=
ilto:Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz">Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz</a>&gt; wrote:<o:p><=
/o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello Raffaella and A=
bigail,</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you for the le=
tter received yesterday at 4:35</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am replying to ack=
nowledge receipt of the letter, and to further acknowledge that Abigail will=
 be copied into all correspondence moving forward.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have requested tha=
t the appointed specialists provide dates and times when they can be availab=
le.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am proposing that t=
he following persons complete site visit, assessing &amp; testing, as a nece=
ssary pre-requisite to providing relevant reports for all stakeholders to re=
view:</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant Metson</spa=
n></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"=
>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Regional Ass=
essing Manager</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Stephen Walker</s=
pan></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0p=
t">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Technical B=
uilding Consultant. ASURNZ.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Warwick Banks</sp=
an></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt=
">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Associate S=
tructural Engineer. CPEng</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Alexandra Dalzell=
</span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11=
.0pt">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Forensi=
c Scientist</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Tyrell Craig</spa=
n></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"=
>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Restoration C=
leaning Specialist.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">LBP Builder</span=
></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=
&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">[ unconfirmed individua=
l ] =E2=80=93 we will require the builder to cut inspection
 holes in the wall linings so testing can be completed within the wall cavit=
ies.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The intention is to t=
est for smoke and chemical contamination within the wall cavities, and on th=
e exposed surfaces downstairs. There will be a significant number of sample s=
ites [tests] to be completed to
 be able to author a reliable report. After initial testing is completed, ou=
r intention is to apply restorative cleaning methods to targeted individual s=
ample sites, followed by subsequent testing, post-cleaning, to provide data t=
o measure the effectiveness
 of cleaning/decontamination.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">All samples taken fr=
om site will require laboratory analysis before being incorporated into a re=
port. This process may take up to 10 working days =E2=80=93 so we want to ca=
pture swab samples from surfaces before and
 after the decontamination process is undertaken.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">At this stage we are=
 looking like being able to conduct this testing onsite, as well as CPEng si=
te visit for assessment, on Friday October 17. Time to yet be confirmed.</sp=
an><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am unsure from you=
r letter attached whether Raffaella and/or other nominated parties wish to b=
e present while this testing and assessment is being conducted. Can you plea=
se confirm for me so that I can complete
 arrangements that will suit all parties who need to be present.</span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Many Thanks,</span><=
o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant.</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
